            "name": "Creed: Rise to Glory™",
            "steam_appid": 804490,
            "required_age": 0,
            "is_free": false,
            "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Train. Fight. Win.</i></strong></h2>Got what it takes to become a champion? You are Adonis Creed, fighting toe-to-toe with the world’s top opponents to establish your boxing legacy. This intense cinematic experience features new Phantom Melee Technology for impactful VR melee combat so you can train, fight, and win like Creed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Live Your Legacy</i></strong></h2>Challenge both your body and mind as you experience the ascent of Adonis Creed from undiscovered underdog to world-class fighter, all within an immersive universe inspired by the Creed™ films.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Multiple Game Modes</i></strong></h2>Choose your path to glory in multiple games modes: store-driven Career, customizable Freeplay, or minigame-based Training.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Online PvP </i></strong></h2>PvP just got a lot more personal. Choose your champion, then set up a custom fight with a friend or find your contenders in crossplay Quick Match. Precise upper-body tracking ensures each blow resonates where it lands—on both your opponent and yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Feel the Impact</i></strong></h2>Phantom Melee Technology mimics the real-life effects of throwing and taking punches in the ring, such as the out-of-body sensation of getting knocked out or the fatigue during a long, frantic bout.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Break them―or become them</i></strong></h2>Play or fight the most iconic figures from the Creed™ and Rocky™ universe in Freeplay or PvP, including classic Rocky Balboa, Ivan and Viktor Drago, and more!",
            "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Train. Fight. Win.</i></strong></h2>Got what it takes to become a champion? You are Adonis Creed, fighting toe-to-toe with the world’s top opponents to establish your boxing legacy. This intense cinematic experience features new Phantom Melee Technology for impactful VR melee combat so you can train, fight, and win like Creed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Live Your Legacy</i></strong></h2>Challenge both your body and mind as you experience the ascent of Adonis Creed from undiscovered underdog to world-class fighter, all within an immersive universe inspired by the Creed™ films.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Multiple Game Modes</i></strong></h2>Choose your path to glory in multiple games modes: store-driven Career, customizable Freeplay, or minigame-based Training.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Online PvP </i></strong></h2>PvP just got a lot more personal. Choose your champion, then set up a custom fight with a friend or find your contenders in crossplay Quick Match. Precise upper-body tracking ensures each blow resonates where it lands—on both your opponent and yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Feel the Impact</i></strong></h2>Phantom Melee Technology mimics the real-life effects of throwing and taking punches in the ring, such as the out-of-body sensation of getting knocked out or the fatigue during a long, frantic bout.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Break them―or become them</i></strong></h2>Play or fight the most iconic figures from the Creed™ and Rocky™ universe in Freeplay or PvP, including classic Rocky Balboa, Ivan and Viktor Drago, and more!",
            "short_description": "You are Adonis Creed, fighting toe-to-toe with the world’s top opponents to establish your boxing legacy. This intense cinematic experience features new Phantom Melee Technology for impactful VR melee combat so you can train, fight, and win like Creed.",
            "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
            "reviews": "“... the studio has not only created one of the best VR boxing games, but one of the best boxing games period.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/spotlights/how-survios-creed-rise-to-glory-revolutionizes-vr-melee-combat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Unreal Engine Blog</a><br><br>“The best part of this game is how good it is at making you want to keep playing it.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.androidcentral.com/creed-rise-glory-review-my-body-hurts-and-i-love-it\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Android Central</a><br><br>“It’s brutal, it’s highly responsive, making it the best VR boxing title, and one of the most addictive VR experiences I’ve encountered thus far.”<br>9/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://gamingtrend.com/feature/reviews/todays-gonna-be-hell-creed-rise-to-glory-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gaming Trend</a><br>",
